      • requestAppointmentBtn

        public void requestAppointmentBtn()
        onclick checks if the date spinners are nulled, if not then it checks for a selected doctor. If not, any doctor is selected and requests an appointment with any doctor, otherwise that specific doctor is chosen. adds to the patient history that they requested an appointment

      • requestAccountTermination

      • terminateAccounts

        public void terminateAccounts()
        checks the termination list for all the patients usernames, if it contains one it deletes the relevant patient. afterwards, it clears the list.

      • removeDoctor
